{"tid":2415664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗: 前年區議會選舉很不正常 要研究防止類似事件","createTime":"2021-02-20T12:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T06:47:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"9097d6777825c30d9b9fc7b1fe53882454395efc","tid":2415664,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:09:52.000Z","msg":"新華社連續三日刊登內地學者的訪問，提到香港選舉制度存在不少漏洞，令「愛國者治港」原則未有充分貫徹，認為要堵塞漏洞，確保選舉安全。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗說，前年區議會選舉很不正常，要研究防止類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席羅健熙批評建制派「輸打贏要」，又說改變選舉方法將無法得到港人信任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576593-20210220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576593-20210220.htm&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=9a0cb11d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576593-20210220.htm&h=d5bcc73b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576593-20210220.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ccdade37755edfe478ab80556e7485abddc33cc3","tid":2415664,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a95db777dd57ab485ccc39429c2b8a5380a6f3","tid":2415664,"uid":99642,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"佢地鍾意啦"},{"pid":"5399f6ef8d35f2e259ecb698b31292a51b5030b5","tid":2415664,"uid":202345,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"研究啲咩 點種票？"},{"pid":"a8628bbb145c21b7c779c08c29895a569e192bc5","tid":2415664,"uid":325586,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"輸唔起就唔好選啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl